        <div class="msgSubject">Life Surge VS Speed Surge</div>
        <div class="sm notbold">
          
          Posted: 2010-10-18 15:35:23   | <input type="checkbox" name="quote-1287437723126368381" id="quote-1287437723126368381" class="msgQuoteCheck" onchange="multiQuote2()"/><label for="quote-1287437723126368381" onclick="multiQuote2()"> Quote</label>  | <a href="/forum.html?forum=186&amp;mid=1287437723126368381&amp;post=1&amp;replyto=1287437723126368381&amp;page=1" class="icon-replytothis" rel="nofollow">Reply to Post</a> | <a id="FOLLOW_MID_1287437723126368381" onclick="followToggle('add','1287437723126368381')" href="javascript:" class="icon-follow">Follow</a> 
        </div>
