      <div class="msgContentFrame">I would say it really depends on the mobs you're fighting and the type of party you have set up.... <br /> <br />If your group is grinding off some low level mobs quickly... the stam+ is probably the best since people aren't have ACC issues... <br /> <br />However, if you're finding its tough for the group to kill a mob quickly.. I'd probably switch to the -EVA for the good of the group... <br /> <br />I'm glad you brought up Feint, because I honestly look forward to 'missing' now that I unlocked this ability and its so strong :b <br /> <br />I just hit 21- so I haven't reached Life surge point yet.. when I do though... My opinion may change.. :3<div class="msgSig"><div class="msgSigBar sm">----------------------------</div>Maverik <br />Paradise Oblivion <br />75SMN/41WHM/45BRD/37RNG/75COR <br />Maverick Hawkeye. Kashuan.</div></div>
