      <div class="msgContentFrame">Speed Surge for solo and Life Surge for party. Stamina regen boost only works on self while Eva debuff works for everyone hitting it physically. As a DEX-based LNC I don't really see any difference between Eva debuff-ed or not. Going to stick with Harpoon + 4 Silver Ring for the rest of my LNC life. <br /> <br /><i><span class="sm">Edited, Nov  3rd 2010  7:35pm by Khornette </span></i><div class="msgSig"><div class="msgSigBar sm">----------------------------</div><img src="http://common.zam.com/xivsigs/1807831.png" height="144" width="482" alt="Signature Image" border="0" /></div></div>
